-- Nestle India Gains in Mumbai Trading on Plan to Purchase Local Company
-- Anoop Agrawal
-- 2010-07-01T03:35:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/nestle-india-gains-in-mumbai-trading-on-plan-to-purchase-local-company.html

          
          
             Nestle India Ltd., the unit of the
world’s biggest food company, gained in Mumbai after Chairman
and Managing Director Antonio Helio Waszyk said the company
plans to buy a local company to expand its business and will
announce the acquisition “sooner than later.”   
